enum RtStreamingConn::StopCause
 

Indicates reason why streaming was stopped.

Enumerator:
StOnEndOfData  Stopped after end of data was encountered.
StOnCommand  Stopped after Stop() was called.
StOnSrcError  Stopped after error was encountered.
StOnSnkError  Stopped after error was encountered.
